t-[var(--color-text)]\">Melayu</option></select><i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-xs pointer-events-none\"></i></div><button class=\"md:hidden text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] text-xl transition-colors\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><i class=\"fas fa-bars\"></i></button></div></div></div></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Article\",\"headline\":\"Hướng Dẫn Tối Ưu Hóa Ảnh Sản Phẩm Cho Thương Mại Điện Tử\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-03-17\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-03-17\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"ToolPic\",\"url\":\"https://toolpic.me\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"ToolPic\",\"url\":\"https://toolpic.me\"},\"url\":\"https://toolpic.me/vi/blog/ecommerce-product-image-optimization\",\"mainEntityOfPage\":\"https://toolpic.me/vi/blog/ecommerce-product-image-optimization\"}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"ToolPic\",\"item\":\"https://toolpic.me/vi\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Blog\",\"item\":\"https://toolpic.me/vi/blog\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Hướng Dẫn Tối Ưu Hóa Ảnh Sản Phẩm Cho Thương Mại Điện Tử\",\"item\":\"https://toolpic.me/vi/blog/ecommerce-product-image-optimization\"}]}</script><div class=\"background-grid\"></div><article class=\"max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-16 sm:pt-24 pb-24\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300 mb-8\" href=\"/vi/blog\"><i class=\"fas fa-arrow-left text-xs\"></i>Blog</a><header class=\"mb-12\"><h1 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight mb-4 gradient-text\">Hướng Dẫn Tối Ưu Hóa Ảnh Sản Phẩm Cho Thương Mại Điện Tử</h1><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><i class=\"fas fa-calendar-alt text-xs\"></i>17 tháng 3, 2026</span><span class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-text-muted)]\"></span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><i class=\"fas fa-clock text-xs\"></i>Đọc 6 phút</span></div></header><div class=\"mb-12 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"/blog/ecommerce-images-hero.jpg\" alt=\"Hướng Dẫn Tối Ưu Hóa Ảnh Sản Phẩm Cho Thương Mại Điện Tử\" class=\"w-full h-auto\"/></div><div class=\"space-y-10\"><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-[var(--color-text)]\">Why Product Images Drive Sales</h2><div class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-[1.8] text-[1.05rem] whitespace-pre-line\">In e-commerce, product images are your most powerful sales tool. Studies show that 75% of online shoppers rely on product photos when making purchase decisions. High-quality images build trust, reduce return rates, and directly increase conversion rates.</div></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-[var(--color-text)]\">Recommended Sizes and Formats</h2><div class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-[1.8] text-[1.05rem] whitespace-pre-line\">For main product images, use dimensions between 1000 and 2000 pixels on the longest side. This provides enough resolution for zoom functionality without being excessively large. Most e-commerce platforms recommend 1200 x 1200 or 1500 x 1500 pixels for square product images.</div></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-[var(--color-text)]\">Image SEO for E-commerce</h2><div class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-[1.8] text-[1.05rem] whitespace-pre-line\">Search engines cannot see your images, but they read the text you associate with them. jpg provide no useful information.</div></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-[var(--color-text)]\">Optimizing Product Images with ToolPic</h2><div class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-[1.8] text-[1.05rem] whitespace-pre-line\">Start by cropping your product photos to a consistent aspect ratio using ToolPic&#x27;s Image Crop tool. Square crops (1:1) work best for most e-commerce platforms and ensure a clean, uniform grid layout in category pages. Crop tightly around the product to maximize the visual impact at smaller display sizes.</div></section></div><div class=\"mt-16 pt-10 border-t border-[var(--color-border)]\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-2\"><i class=\"fas fa-wrench text-[var(--color-purple)]\"></i>Công cụ liên quan</h3><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><a class=\"glass-card p-5 block hover:border-[var(--color-border-hover)] transition-all duration-300 group\" href=\"/vi/tools/nen-anh\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-purple)]/10 to-[var(--color-blue)]/10 flex items-center justify-center\"><i class=\"fas fa-compress text-sm text-[var(--color-text)]\"></i></div><h4 class=\"font-semibold group-hover:text-[var(--color-purple)] transition-colors\">Nen hinh anh</h4></div><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed\">Nen anh JPEG, PNG, WebP len den 80% ma khong mat chat luong.</p></a><a class=\"glass-card p-5 block hover:border-[var(--color-border-hover)] transition-all duration-300 group\" href=\"/vi/tools/cat-anh\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-purple)]/10 to-[var(--color-blue)]/10 flex items-center justify-center\"><i class=\"fas fa-crop text-sm text-[var(--color-text)]\"></i></div><h4 class=\"font-semibold group-hover:text-[var(--color-purple)] transition-colors\">Cat va thay doi kich thuoc anh</h4></div><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed\">Cat va thay doi kich thuoc anh voi kich thuoc dat san cho mang xa hoi.</p></a></div></div></article><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-[#040405] border-t border-[var(--color-border)] mt-20\"><div class=\"max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-16 pb-8\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr_1fr_1fr] gap-10 mb-12\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><span class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-purple)] to-[var(--color-blue)] flex items-center justify-center\"><i class=\"fas fa-wand-magic-sparkles text-white text-base\"></i></span><span class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">ToolPic</span></div><p class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] max-w-[300px] leading-relaxed\">Cong cu truc tuyen mien phi cho hinh anh va video. 100% trong trinh duyet, tep cua ban khong bao gio roi khoi thiet bi.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-4\">Cong cu</h3><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li><a class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/vi/tools/image-compressor\">Nen hinh anh</a></li><li><a class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/vi/tools/image-converter\">Chuyen doi hinh anh</a></li><li><a class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/vi/tools/image-crop\">Cat va thay doi kich thuoc anh</a></li><li><a class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/vi/tools/image-watermark\">Them watermark</a></li><li><a class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/vi/tools/image-bg-remove\">Xoa nen anh</a></li><li><a class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/vi/tools/video-compress\">Nen video</a></li><li><a class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)]